casebody.data:
Auerbach et al., Appellants, v. McGovern, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 18, 1890.) Appeal from eleventh district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

C. E. Davison, for appellants. A. Lamont, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
